<aside class="client-callout" aria-label="UHID rules">
  <p class="client-callout__title">UHID — Unique Health Identifier</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Assigned at sign-up</strong> — before the first diagnostic order</li>
    <li><strong>Globally unique</strong> within Zenlife · never reused</li>
    <li><strong>Permanent</strong> — unchanged if mobile, name, or address updates</li>
    <li><strong>Visible</strong> on profile, orders, appointments, and Zen reports</li>
    <li><strong>Not</strong> the mobile number, email, or internal database key</li>
  </ul>
</aside>
